name: MrsPepe
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The smart contract is not verified for the following asset, which means the owners may be able to modify contract behaviour (for example: disable selling, change fees, mint new tokens, or transfer tokens). Please proceed with caution.

description.en:
What is the project about?
MrsPepe is here to make memes great again, she is Pepe's wife, she is a community token, with a truly fantastic community, she is super loved and everyone is working to grow day by day, with so many whales and networks of amazing people who are pushing the project non-stop, the number of members on social networks and the number of holders is continuously increasing and the hype is getting bigger and bigger, many big names, including influencers and callers are actively investing and sponsoring the project, the numbers are excellent and are getting better and better, it is certainly a project that if it continues in this way is destined for great successes.

What makes your project unique?
Mrspepe is a meme token following the pepe trend 
Tends to introduce huge utility as we expand.

History of your project.

MrsPepe (Popa) is tired of watching Pepe get all the attention whilst it was her who helped him make meme-coins great again. She adores her husband Pepe but also has decided its time to get In the limelight.
What’s next for your project?
We have a lot of marketing planned out and already started and also we have influencers on board 
What can your token be used for?
